<span style="margin-left: 0in;"><span class="AuthorDate"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;">Tickell</span></span>, Oxford University, journalist, environmental researcher and activist specializing in global warming, <span class="AuthorDate"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;">‘8</span></span></span>
